page.title: 15A 12YRS.OLD MUSICAL INTEREST
page.content: On saturday mornings I play with the Exeter Childrens Orchestra & we play for 2 hrs.I go with my cousin and friend,they play flutes & I play the clarinet & my best friend also plays the clarinet.We are in the first clarinets which means we play harder music than in second clarinets.I often play in cocerts,in Exeter & sometimes in other towns.The music we play varies from classical to jazz.Our composer composes music which is quite lively.The instruments in the orchestra range from records to a harp.There are over 100 members of the orchestra,all of us love our conductors dog,especially when he dresses her up for concerts and discos.
